Hitachi, Mitsubishi Heavy Industries Said to Discuss Merger of Some Units

-- B y   Y o s h i n o r i   E k i
-- 
2011-08-03T21:54:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-03/hitachi-mitsubishi-heavy-industries-said-to-discuss-merger-of-some-units.html
Hitachi Ltd. (6501)  and  Mitsubishi Heavy
Industries Ltd. (7011)  agreed to discuss a merger of some businesses,
including infrastructure, a person familiar with the matter
said, confirming an earlier Nikkei newspaper report. The
companies plan to announce details today, the person said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yoshinori Eki in Tokyo at 
 yeki@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
